_analyzer.py\n152: - [ ] AC014: Kubernetes deployment wires secrets and environment variables correctly\n153: - [ ] AC015: SDK exceptions (CommandExecutionError) are properly handled\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Verification Commands\n158: \n159: ```bash\n160: # Plugin structure verification\n161: ls -la integrations/dify-plugin/\n162: ls -la integrations/dify-plugin/provider/\n163: ls -la integrations/dify-plugin/tools/\n164: \n165: # PCAP analyzer build\n166: docker build -f example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile -t pcap-analyzer:test .\n167: \n168: # PCAP analyzer run\n169: docker run -p 8000:8000 \\\n170:   -e OPENAI_API_KEY=$OPENAI_API_KEY \\\n171:   -e ROUTER_URL=http://router:8080 \\\n172:   -e WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workload-manager:8080 \\\n173:   pcap-analyzer:test\n174: \n175: # Test analyze endpoint (with file)\n176: curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/analyze \\\n177:   -F \"pcap_file=@capture.pcap\"\n178: \n179: # Test analyze endpoint (with path)\n180: curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/analyze \\\n181:   -F \"pcap_path=/data/capture.pcap\"\n182: ```\n\n(End of file - total 182 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-036: Dify 插件集成\n\n**Module:** integrations  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Dify Plugin Package Structure\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `integrations/dify-plugin/` directory structure\n- [ ] **T002** Create `integrations/dify-plugin/main.py` with entry point `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()`\n- [ ] **T003** Create `integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml` with required Dify plugin metadata (version 0.0.2, type plugin, author volcano-sh, name agentcube, labels, icons, resources)\n- [ ] **T004** Create `integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` with `dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0` and `agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10`\n- [ ] **T005** Create `integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore` file\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Plugin Icons","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspa